---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Matthew's Yard Services | Professional Landscape Maintenance & Lawn Care | Midlothian, VA">
  <main class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Matthew's Yard Services</h1>
      <p>Delivering exceptional landscape maintenance and lawn care services throughout Chesterfield County and surrounding areas. From residential lawns to commercial landscapes, we provide reliable, detail-oriented service that enhances your property's value and curb appeal.</p>
      <div class="hero-badges">
        <span class="badge">🏆 5+ Years Professional Experience</span>
        <span class="badge">📍 Based in Midlothian, VA</span>
      </div>
      <a href="/estimate" class="button">Request Free Estimate</a>
    </div>

    <div class="services">
      <h2>Professional Landscape Services</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🌱</div>
          <h3>Lawn Mowing & Maintenance</h3>
          <p>Professional weekly or bi-weekly mowing services with precision edging, string trimming, and debris removal. We maintain consistent cut heights and patterns for optimal lawn health and appearance.</p>
          <span class="price-range">Starting at $35 per visit</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🌿</div>
          <h3>Landscape Bed Maintenance</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive garden bed care including hand-weeding, plant pruning, deadheading, and soil cultivation. We maintain the health and aesthetics of your planted areas year-round.</p>
          <span class="price-range">Starting at $30 per hour</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🌳</div>
          <h3>Mulching & Soil Enhancement</h3>
          <p>Professional mulch installation and soil amendments to improve plant health, retain moisture, and enhance visual appeal. We use premium materials and proper application techniques.</p>
          <span class="price-range">Custom pricing available</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🍂</div>
          <h3>Seasonal Property Cleanup</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive spring and fall cleanup services including leaf removal, debris clearing, flower bed preparation, and seasonal plantings to maintain your property year-round.</p>
          <span class="price-range">Starting at $175 per cleanup</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">✂️</div>
          <h3>Shrub & Tree Trimming</h3>
          <p>Expert pruning and shaping of ornamental shrubs, hedges, and small trees. We follow proper horticultural practices to promote healthy growth and maintain desired shapes.</p>
          <span class="price-range">Starting at $25 per shrub</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-note">
        <p><strong>📋 Customized Service Packages:</strong> We design maintenance programs tailored to your property's specific needs and your budget. All estimates include detailed scope of work and transparent pricing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="gallery">
      <h2>Project Portfolio</h2>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="before-after">
            <div class="before">
              <span class="label">BEFORE</span>
